  <h1>üèÅ SUI Cars Whitepaper</h1>

  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    SUI Cars is a blockchain-based play-to-earn game where players own NFT cars with different rarities and earn rewards by racing. Built on the Sui blockchain, the game brings together NFTs, daily gameplay, and on-chain rewards.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Vision</h2>
  <p>
    Our mission is to create a sustainable and engaging Web3 game where owning and upgrading your cars leads to real rewards and community value.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Gameplay Overview</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Each car is an NFT with one of 3 rarities: <strong>Common</strong>, <strong>Hybrid</strong>, and <strong>Electric</strong>.</li>
    <li>Cars can be raced daily to earn rewards based on their rarity and a touch of randomness.</li>
    <li>The better your car, the higher your daily earning potential.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Rarity System</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Rarity</th>
        <th>Color</th>
