  <h2>5. Earning System</h2>
  <p>
    Cars can race once per day. The rewards are distributed in the native token (to be announced). The better the rarity, the higher the reward multiplier.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Minting Process</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>NFTs will be minted directly via <strong>Tradeport</strong> on the Sui blockchain.</li>
    <li>Total supply: <strong>10,000 NFTs</strong></li>
    <li>Mint date: To be announced on our Twitter & website.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Tokenomics (Future Feature)</h2>
  <p>
    A native token may be introduced for in-game upgrades, marketplace use, and staking.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Wallet Support</h2>
  <p>
    Users can connect with <strong>Slush</strong> and <strong>Phantom Wallets</strong>. Wallet integration is done using the <a href="https://github.com/wallet-standard" target="_blank">wallet-standard</a> approach on Sui.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Team</h2>
  <p>
    Anonymous team with experience in Web3, gaming, and NFTs. Operating with transparency and focusing on delivering fun and utility.
  </p>

